      <title>摩根大通称印度必须修复经济管道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/india-has-to-fix-plumbing-of-economy-jpmorgan-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通首席印度经济学家 Sajjid Z. Chinoy 表示，印度政府必须找到除税收以外的新方法来创造收入来源。他在彭博特别网络研讨会上与彭博电视台的 Menaka Doshi 讨论了新的联邦预算（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/india-has-to-fix-plumbing-of-economy-jpmorgan-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石抵押信托公司将股息削减 24%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/blackstone-mortgage-trust-cuts-dividend-by-24-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为商业房地产提供融资的黑石抵押贷款信托公司 (Blackstone Mortgage Trust Inc.) 正在削减 24% 的股息，因为违约率上升，借款人难以偿还贷款或再融资。彭博社观点栏目 (Bloomberg Opinion) 的 Nir ​​Kaissar 在“彭博公开利息” (Bloomberg Open Interest) 节目中进一步谈论了黑石的困境。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-24/blackstone-mortgage-trust-cuts-dividend-by-24-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前英国央行官员预测劳工税将上涨至 250 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ex-boe-official-predicts-labour-tax-hikes-as-high-as-25-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行前政策制定者迈克尔·桑德斯表示，英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯可以利用对工党财政遗产的即将进行的审查，来证明在即将到来的预算中增税高达 250 亿英镑（323 亿美元）的合理性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ex-boe-official-predicts-labour-tax-hikes-as-high-as-25-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 13:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯将在 2024 年至 2025 年期间延续 OPEC+ 补偿减产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/russia-to-spread-opec-compensation-oil-cuts-through-2024-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯计划在今年 10 月和 11 月以及 2025 年 3 月至 9 月期间额外削减原油产量，以弥补超过 OPEC+ 配额的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/russia-to-spread-opec-compensation-oil-cuts-through-2024-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 12:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司因债务减少而避免罚款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/moody-s-cuts-thames-water-s-highest-ranked-bonds-to-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司请求监管机构帮助其避免巨额罚款，此前其最优先债务被穆迪评级下调为垃圾债，这进一步加大了英国最大供水商的财务压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/moody-s-cuts-thames-water-s-highest-ranked-bonds-to-junk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 11:29:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>家居用品零售商 Conn’s 因销售额下滑申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/retailer-conn-s-files-for-bankruptcy-following-sales-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[家具零售商 Conn’s Inc. 申请破产并计划关闭，原因是整合最近的收购事件遇到困难，加剧了销售滞后的痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/retailer-conn-s-files-for-bankruptcy-following-sales-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:55:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
